For the Positions.txt
    Select the required value. Note that selection may dissapear at a given moment.
    Pose and Joints update every 5 seconds.

For auto replacements
    Type ${currentp} in your script file to get it automaticly replaced with the current pose.
    Type ${currentj} in your script file to get it automaticly replaced with the current joint.

    Wait for +-5 seconds for it to update.
    
    Example:

        HomePosition = ${currentp}
        movej(HomePosition)